1337
01:35:33,060 --> 01:35:38,340
[SPEAKER_00] I to radi, NFT ne radi, nema nikakvu realnu primjenu.

1338
01:35:38,340 --> 01:35:42,340
[SPEAKER_00] Koristiš još neki drugi alat u poslu osim ChardGPT-a?

1339
01:35:42,340 --> 01:35:49,340
[SPEAKER_00] Koristim neke alate koji su bazirane opet na ChardGPT-u, ali najviše koristim ChardGPT.

1340
